a:7:{s:5:"posts";a:250:{i:0;a:23:{s:2:"ID";s:1:"6";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2016-12-07 12:23:54";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2016-12-07 12:23:54";s:12:"post_content";s:5701:"[vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_promo type="default" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" title_style="default" title_align="center" title="Our Support Policy" subtitle="" description="" link="" link_text="" link_image="" link2="" link2_text="" text_bg_color="" image="" image_position="left" image_width="50%" image_cover="1" image_bg_color="" size="large" text_width="none" text_float="none" text_align="none" full_height="" text_paddings="" text_margins="" gap="" scheme="inherit" id="" class="" css=""][vc_empty_space height="" alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_dot">
	<li>To get a pre-purchase advice, you may post in the theme’s forum.</li>
	<li>To get a response more promptly, you are recommended to use our Ticket-system.</li>
	<li>We try to answer your questions within 1-10 hours. However, if any delay occurs, it doesn’t mean that we forgot about you. Some of the issues require testing and analyzing, so we can resolve it effectively.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_dot">
	<li>Please note! We do not provide support, if you do not have the purchase code.</li>
	<li>Item support does not include:
<ol>
	<li>Customization and installation.</li>
	<li>Support for third party software and plugins.</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/trx_sc_promo][vc_separator style="dashed"][trx_sc_promo type="default" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" title_style="default" title_align="center" title="How to use our Support System" subtitle="" description="" link="" link_text="" link_image="" link2="" link2_text="" text_bg_color="" image="" image_position="left" image_width="50%" image_cover="1" image_bg_color="" size="large" text_width="none" text_float="none" text_align="none" full_height="" text_paddings="" text_margins="" gap="" scheme="inherit" id="" class="" css=""][vc_empty_space height="" alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="7" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
	<li>In the ‘Item Details’ there is a clickable banner “Support Sys”, which leads you to tickets.</li>
	<li>Or you may simply follow this link: <a href="http://ancorathemes.ticksy.com">ancorathemes.ticksy.com</a>.</li>
	<li>Enter your purchase key and register in the system.</li>
	<li>To avoid a confusion, please use your own ThemeForest login in Support System.</li>
	<li>Fill out the ticket form.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/trx_sc_promo][vc_separator style="dashed"][trx_sc_promo type="default" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" title_style="default" title_align="center" title="How to find a purchase key" subtitle="" description="" link="" link_text="" link_image="" link2="" link2_text="" text_bg_color="" image="" image_position="left" image_width="50%" image_cover="1" image_bg_color="" size="large" text_width="none" text_float="none" text_align="none" full_height="" text_paddings="" text_margins="" gap="" scheme="inherit" id="" class="" css=""][vc_empty_space height="" alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="8" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
	<li>Open the “downloads” tab in your account.</li>
	<li>Find our theme in the list of products.</li>
	<li>Click “download” button, and in the drop-down menu select “license certificate &amp; purchase code”.</li>
</ol>

<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Acupuncture Is A Form Of
Alternative Medicine</h3>
A key component of traditional Chinese medicine (TCM). TCM theory and practice are not based upon scientific knowledge, and acupuncture is a pseudoscience with  diverse rangeof theories.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522290366{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hypnotherapy" tab_id="1481199504140-8a77dfa0-620d"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="186" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
During hypnosis, a person is said to have heightened focus and concentration. The person can concentrate intensely on a specific thought or memory, while blocking out sources of distraction.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522285392{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Chiropractic" tab_id="1482922426243-790f2190-d252"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Chiropractic Is Treatment
Of The Spine</h3>
The main chiropractic treatment technique involves manual therapy, especially spinal manipulation therapy (SMT), manipulations of other joints and soft tissues. Its foundation is at odds with mainstream medicine.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522343652{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Massage" tab_id="1482922460984-cfe74733-07d7"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Massage For A Better
Body Performance</h3>
Involves working and acting on the body with pressure – structured, unstructured, stationary, or moving – tension, motion, or vibration, done manually or with mechanical aids.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522349719{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Physiotherapy" tab_id="1482922478624-de10010d-d4b2"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="42" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
A medicine and rehabilitation specialty that, by using mechanical force and movements, remediates impairments and promotes mobility, function, and quality of life through examination, diagnosis, and physical intervention.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522356288{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Reflexology" tab_id="1482922491399-dba3164d-7a6a"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="63" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Reflexology Is Pressure
Zone Therapy</h3>
Application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion. It is based on a system of zones and reflex areas that purportedly reflect an image of the body.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522362424{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1482923596477{padding-top: 7.3em !important;padding-bottom: 10.55em !important;}"][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_align="center" title="Benefits of Hypnosis" subtitle="" description="" scheme="inherit" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1482923397735{margin-bottom: 4.4em !important;}" title_tag="none" link="" link_text="" link_image=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482923389126{padding-right: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]The hypnotic state allows a person to be more open to discussion and suggestion. It can improve the success of other treatments for many conditions.
<ul>
 	<li>Hypnosis can help people change their eating behaviors and drop the pounds</li>
 	<li>Cognitive hypnotherapy helps change unwanted patterns and behaviors by connecting with the subconscious mind</li>
 	<li>Hypnosis has been used to treat chronic types of pain and pain resulting from serious injury</li>
 	<li>Hypnosis gives your mind and body a chance to recuperate, repair and heal itself by experiencing the relaxation that it desperately needs</li>
 	<li>Hypnosis can help treat the psychological problem that is causing the sleep disturbance while at the same time it puts the body in a deeply relaxed state that helps the body and mind become rejuvenated</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Sip Cold Water and Eat
Small Meals</h3>
Sipping cold water through a straw can help replace the act of sucking on a cigarette. It also releases dopamine, a feel-good brain chemical that can help ease bad moods, research shows.

Eating small meals can also help you get past the urge to smoke. Choose lean, healthy foods to avoid weight gain.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/trx_slide][trx_slide title="" subtitle="" link="" image="" video_url="" video_embed="" id="" class="" css=""][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="213" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482923277737{padding-left: 5em !important;}"]

<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Sip Cold Water and Eat
Small Meals</h3>
Sipping cold water through a straw can help replace the act of sucking on a cigarette. It also releases dopamine, a feel-good brain chemical that can help ease bad moods, research shows.

Eating small meals can also help you get past the urge to smoke. Choose lean, healthy foods to avoid weight gain.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/trx_slide][trx_slide title="" subtitle="" link="" image="" video_url="" video_embed="" id="" class="" css=""][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="213" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482923277737{padding-left: 5em !important;}"]

Fresh Air</h3>
Sipping cold water through a straw can help replace the act of sucking on a cigarette. It also releases dopamine, a feel-good brain chemical that can help ease bad moods, research shows.

Eating small meals can also help you get past the urge to smoke. <h5><span style="color: #84b5b4;">"Positive thinking will let you do everything better than negative thinking will."</span></h5>
My name is Edward Carter and I have been a full-time professional hypnotherapist since 1987. I am currently registered as a Senior Practitioner on the Hypnotherapy Register. Since launching a private practice in New York I have personally helped hundreds of people from all over East Coast.

Being a hypnotherapist is great. Most clients are new to the subject and do not know how much - or how quickly - hypnosis can help them. Whenever possible, I will get rid of their problem in just one session. This naturally amazes people, especially if they have had the problem for many years. Some problems might take longer to eliminate but the only way to find out is to start!

For more information call <span style="color: #fbc36c;">1 (800) 123 4567</span> now. Quisque dui mi, imperdiet et elementum non, varius eget ex.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_single_image image="246" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1482495199363{margin-top: 3.8em !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_layouts type="default" layout="486" id="" class="" css=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1482766636418{padding-top: 7.2em !important;padding-bottom: 9.75em !important;background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_align="center" title="How Does Hypnosis Work?" subtitle="" description="" scheme="inherit" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1482766241485{margin-bottom: 4.2em !important;}" title_tag="none" link="" link_text="" link_image=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="7/12"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full" style="vc_box_rounded" css=".vc_custom_1482826298290{padding-right: 5em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/12"][vc_column_text]During hypnosis, your body relaxes and your thoughts become more focused. Like other relaxation techniques, hypnosis lowers blood pressure and heart rate, and changes certain types of brain wave activity. In this relaxed state, you will feel at ease physically yet fully awake mentally, and you may be highly responsive to suggestion. Your conscious mind becomes less alert and your subconscious mind becomes more focused.

There are several stages of hypnosis:
<ul class="trx_addons_list_dot">
 	<li>Reframing the problem</li>
 	<li>Becoming relaxed, then absorbed (deeply engaged in the words or images presented by a hypnotherapist)</li>
 	<li>Dissociating (letting go of critical thoughts)</li>
 	<li>Responding (complying with a hypnotherapist's suggestions)</li>
 	<li>Returning to usual awareness</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Acupuncture Is A Form Of
Alternative Medicine</h3>
A key component of traditional Chinese medicine (TCM). TCM theory and practice are not based upon scientific knowledge, and acupuncture is a pseudoscience with  diverse rangeof theories.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522309090{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hypnotherapy" tab_id="1481199504140-8a77dfa0-620d"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="186" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
During hypnosis, a person is said to have heightened focus and concentration. The person can concentrate intensely on a specific thought or memory, while blocking out sources of distraction.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522279960{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Chiropractic" tab_id="1482922426243-790f2190-d252"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Chiropractic Is Treatment
Of The Spine</h3>
The main chiropractic treatment technique involves manual therapy, especially spinal manipulation therapy (SMT), manipulations of other joints and soft tissues. Its foundation is at odds with mainstream medicine.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522315565{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Massage" tab_id="1482922460984-cfe74733-07d7"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Massage For A Better
Body Performance</h3>
Involves working and acting on the body with pressure – structured, unstructured, stationary, or moving – tension, motion, or vibration, done manually or with mechanical aids.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522323500{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Physiotherapy" tab_id="1482922478624-de10010d-d4b2"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="42" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Physiotherapy For
Functional Activities</h3>
A medicine and rehabilitation specialty that, by using mechanical force and movements, remediates impairments and promotes mobility, function, and quality of life through examination, diagnosis, and physical intervention.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522330869{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Reflexology" tab_id="1482922491399-dba3164d-7a6a"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="63" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Reflexology Is Pressure
Zone Therapy</h3>
Application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion. It is based on a system of zones and reflex areas that purportedly reflect an image of the body.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522336962{margin-top: <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Acupuncture Is A Form Of
Alternative Medicine</h3>
A key component of traditional Chinese medicine (TCM). TCM theory and practice are not based upon scientific knowledge, and acupuncture is a pseudoscience with  diverse rangeof theories.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522309090{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hypnotherapy" tab_id="1481199504140-8a77dfa0-620d"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="186" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
During hypnosis, a person is said to have heightened focus and concentration. The person can concentrate intensely on a specific thought or memory, while blocking out sources of distraction.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522279960{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Chiropractic" tab_id="1482922426243-790f2190-d252"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Chiropractic Is Treatment
Of The Spine</h3>
The main chiropractic treatment technique involves manual therapy, especially spinal manipulation therapy (SMT), manipulations of other joints and soft tissues. Its foundation is at odds with mainstream medicine.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522315565{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Massage" tab_id="1482922460984-cfe74733-07d7"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Massage For A Better
Body Performance</h3>
Involves working and acting on the body with pressure – structured, unstructured, stationary, or moving – tension, motion, or vibration, done manually or with mechanical aids.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522323500{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Physiotherapy" tab_id="1482922478624-de10010d-d4b2"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="42" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Physiotherapy For
Functional Activities</h3>
A medicine and rehabilitation specialty that, by using mechanical force and movements, remediates impairments and promotes mobility, function, and quality of life through examination, diagnosis, and physical intervention.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522330869{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Reflexology" tab_id="1482922491399-dba3164d-7a6a"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="63" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Reflexology Is Pressure
Zone Therapy</h3>
Application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion. It is based on a system of zones and reflex areas that purportedly reflect an image of the body.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522336962{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][trx_sc_layouts type="default" layout="560" id="" <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Acupuncture Is A Form Of
Alternative Medicine</h3>
A key component of traditional Chinese medicine (TCM). TCM theory and practice are not based upon scientific knowledge, and acupuncture is a pseudoscience with  diverse rangeof theories.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522309090{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hypnotherapy" tab_id="1481199504140-8a77dfa0-620d"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="186" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
During hypnosis, a person is said to have heightened focus and concentration. The person can concentrate intensely on a specific thought or memory, while blocking out sources of distraction.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522279960{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Chiropractic" tab_id="1482922426243-790f2190-d252"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Chiropractic Is Treatment
Of The Spine</h3>
The main chiropractic treatment technique involves manual therapy, especially spinal manipulation therapy (SMT), manipulations of other joints and soft tissues. Its foundation is at odds with mainstream medicine.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522315565{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Massage" tab_id="1482922460984-cfe74733-07d7"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Massage For A Better
Body Performance</h3>
Involves working and acting on the body with pressure – structured, unstructured, stationary, or moving – tension, motion, or vibration, done manually or with mechanical aids.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522323500{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Physiotherapy" tab_id="1482922478624-de10010d-d4b2"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="42" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Physiotherapy For
Functional Activities</h3>
A medicine and rehabilitation specialty that, by using mechanical force and movements, remediates impairments and promotes mobility, function, and quality of life through examination, diagnosis, and physical intervention.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522330869{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Reflexology" tab_id="1482922491399-dba3164d-7a6a"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="63" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Reflexology Is Pressure
Zone Therapy</h3>
Application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion. It is based on a system of zones and reflex areas that purportedly reflect an image of the body.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522336962{margin-top: <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Acupuncture Is A Form Of
Alternative Medicine</h3>
A key component of traditional Chinese medicine (TCM). TCM theory and practice are not based upon scientific knowledge, and acupuncture is a pseudoscience with  diverse rangeof theories.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522309090{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hypnotherapy" tab_id="1481199504140-8a77dfa0-620d"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="186" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Hypnosis Is A State Of
Focused Relaxation</h3>
During hypnosis, a person is said to have heightened focus and concentration. The person can concentrate intensely on a specific thought or memory, while blocking out sources of distraction.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522279960{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Chiropractic" tab_id="1482922426243-790f2190-d252"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="74" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Chiropractic Is Treatment
Of The Spine</h3>
The main chiropractic treatment technique involves manual therapy, especially spinal manipulation therapy (SMT), manipulations of other joints and soft tissues. Its foundation is at odds with mainstream medicine.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522315565{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Massage" tab_id="1482922460984-cfe74733-07d7"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Massage For A Better
Body Performance</h3>
Involves working and acting on the body with pressure – structured, unstructured, stationary, or moving – tension, motion, or vibration, done manually or with mechanical aids.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522323500{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Physiotherapy" tab_id="1482922478624-de10010d-d4b2"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="42" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Physiotherapy For
Functional Activities</h3>
A medicine and rehabilitation specialty that, by using mechanical force and movements, remediates impairments and promotes mobility, function, and quality of life through examination, diagnosis, and physical intervention.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522330869{margin-top: 3em !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Reflexology" tab_id="1482922491399-dba3164d-7a6a"][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="63" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1482922406036{padding-left: 5em !important;}"][vc_column_text]
<h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Reflexology Is Pressure
Zone Therapy</h3>
Application of pressure to the feet and hands with specific thumb, finger, and hand techniques without the use of oil or lotion. It is based on a system of zones and reflex areas that purportedly reflect an image of the body.[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_button type="filled" size="large" link="/appointments/" title="Request Appointment" subtitle="" align="none" text_align="none" back_image="" icon_type="fontawesome" icon_fontawesome="" image="" icon_position="left" id="" class="" css=".vc_custom_1483522336962{margin-top:
